Package net.shawfire.scs

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SysInDelegate
    SysInDelegate provided a mechanism by which the readLine routine can be replace for testing purposes.
    SysOutDelegate
    SysOutDelegate provided a mechanism by which the println routine can be replace for testing purposes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActivityFuelLookup
    ActivityFuelLookup enum class provides a lookup to determine the corresponding fuel usage based on the SquareType in the SiteMap.
    App
    This is the main App for the site clearing simulation.
    Bulldozer
    The Bulldozer class accepts a siteMap within the constructor.
    Command
    This class is used to read a command from the input stream.
    CommandPojo
    As the `Advance` command also has a corresponding amount the `CommandPojo` is used which supports an `Optional` `amount`.
    Constants
    Application constants: Messages, Prompts and Labels.
    Costs
    The Costs class enables incrementing quantities of on ItemType.
    ItemCostLookup
    ItemCostLookup provides a lookup for ItemType costs per individual item.
    SiteMap
    `SiteMap` is a class which contains a grid of `SquareType` (siteMap).
    Utils
    Utils encapsulated some generic static functions like printing which requires an abstraction for testing with mockito mocks.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ChangeInDirection
    Enum representing a change in direction (`LEFT` or `RIGHT`) for the bulldozer.
    CommandType
    CommandType is an enum class for Command Types.
    Direction
    Direction enum provides a mechanism to change the direction left or right the four different direction orientations namely: `EAST`, `SOUTH`, `WEST`, and `NORTH`
    ItemType
    ItemType enum contains all the categories for which quantities and costs are calculated.
    SquareType
    SquareType enum provides the type that is used to store state of each location on the SiteMap.
